  @contract  resolves same-onset plan collisions in a per-column plan list (mutates in place)  @ 332
  @invariant  fromLogical is monotone but not isotone; two logical onsets can round onto one raw ppq  @ 333
  @contract  later-source-ppq plan (curr by tie-break) shifts up 1 ppq, else predecessor shifts back  @ 334
